01:21:32,722 --> 01:21:34,599
- Kapten!
- Ayo!

897
01:21:46,736 --> 01:21:47,737
Lindungi aku!

898
01:21:48,696 --> 01:21:49,697
Kapten!

899
01:21:52,742 --> 01:21:55,036
- Ayo!
- Ayo!

